WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:05.999
Hey, good morning, family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.947
Well, I just want to thank every single one of you again. Thank you for coming.

00:00:10.948 --> 00:00:16.279
Every single time we do a video, you come out and you pray. You take things seriously.

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:25.180
This is where I've been. I told the Lord, I said, "I don't want to be where I'm at today this way tomorrow.

00:00:25.181 --> 00:00:34.413
I'm tired of being just the status quo. I'm tired of the status quo. I'm tired of Christianity as usual.

00:00:34.414 --> 00:00:43.746
I'm ready for Christianity unusual."This is why when you get fed up being the way you are, that's when you'll start to see change.

00:00:43.747 --> 00:00:49.359
I want change. Diana and I, Braden, Megan, all of us. I want change in my daughter.

00:00:49.360 --> 00:00:59.309
I want change in my family. I want change, expecting God to do something big in your life. And I said, "Lord, I want the revival.

00:00:59.310 --> 00:01:07.491
I want healings, demonstrations, and manifestations of your glory in these last days. You said we would walk in this.

00:01:07.492 --> 00:01:29.556
Where's the kink in the hose?"And the Bible says, "If ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will."But it's about remaining in this word and getting this word's foundation in your life, the love walk, going back to 1 Corinthians 13 and meditating on what He said.

00:01:29.557 --> 00:01:59.171
Getting that word, the love, because the glory of what He said, Brandon—the glory of those big silos of that honey glow—was connected to love, getting a love foundation in your life from 1 Corinthians 13, meditating on that, and getting that word of what the Bible says about love taking no account of a suffered wrong when people do you wrong and all these things, but also believing God that He's going to do it.

00:01:59.172 --> 00:02:05.767
Having an expectation for manifestations, because expectation brings the manifestation.

00:02:05.768 --> 00:02:13.829
I believe that God is going to show up in this service tomorrow for your churches, or for wherever you have a church or prayer group.

00:02:13.830 --> 00:02:19.341
I expect for us to get something radical from the Holy Spirit today.

00:02:19.342 --> 00:02:30.717
I do not want to go away and have another lukewarm service that everybody kind of feels was okay, whatever, bypassing another week.

00:02:30.718 --> 00:02:38.179
I know from glory to glory He's changing me. I want that so bad.

00:02:38.180 --> 00:02:47.312
The only thing that's ever going to change you is having a foundation of this word down inside of your heart, changing you from the inside out.

00:02:47.313 --> 00:02:51.802
That's the only thing. And that's what Brother Hagin—he drove it home.

00:02:51.803 --> 00:02:56.073
That's all he ever talked about: "Faith cometh by hearing, hearing by the word of God,"you know.

00:02:56.075 --> 00:03:01.350
And R.W. Schambach, all the greats. I said, "My goodness, Lord, help me.

00:03:01.351 --> 00:03:07.731
If I'm a closer, I don't want to let these guys down. I don't want to let you down. I want to finish strong.

00:03:07.732 --> 00:03:16.713
Lord, let us do something big for you because the word is working mightily in me. The word is working mightily in me. Do you believe it?

00:03:16.714 --> 00:03:33.963
Do you believe it?"But then He said to me when I was driving around today, He said, "Brandon, I want you to start to believe for manifestations of angelic encounters—not flaky stuff, but truly changing you from the inside out—the word, believing for that.

00:03:33.964 --> 00:03:52.869
But not only that, believing for demonstrations of the Holy Spirit, manifestations of the Holy Spirit, and angelic visitations in your services every day, Lord, by love."I get this love like He said, love from 1 Corinthians 13.

00:03:52.870 --> 00:04:09.637
Get in that love. Okay, so if I'm walking in love, and you are love, and you're inside of me, and I'm inside with you, Lord, and we take this communion every day, and we're expecting for you to show up in the mall, showing up in these circumstances.

00:04:09.638 --> 00:04:24.399
There was a guy, when I had all these things going on with our house, I told you the guy hit our septic, and it was like thousands of dollars to get this septic fixed.

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:33.228
But when he was here, my first reaction was just to lose it, because he just did all this, right?

00:04:33.229 --> 00:04:36.971
And he wasn't going to fix it because I didn't tell him where the septic was.

00:04:36.972 --> 00:04:47.999
So it was, you know, and he said, "I'll go in half."But the Holy Spirit said, "Walk in love. Walk in love. Walk in love. Don't lose it on this man.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:05:08.875
There's more to this than what meets the eye."And so, to make a long story short, another guy came, and he was a Hispanic man, and the Lord said to me, "He does not know me."Witness to him, impart love into him, and talk to him about the word.

00:05:08.876 --> 00:05:13.645
You could feel instantaneously the devil inside of him starts talking out.

00:05:13.646 --> 00:05:18.052
"Are you smoking dope? Are you doing this stuff?"because you're talking about the Holy Ghost.

00:05:18.053 --> 00:05:24.319
You're talking about the end times, "Jesus is coming. The end times are here."I'm just bold about my faith, folks.

00:05:24.320 --> 00:05:30.194
I'm not going to ever just back down. And if the Holy Spirit comes on me, you're going to see a radical evangelist right there.

00:05:30.195 --> 00:05:34.879
And that's what I do. And so I start telling him about the Antichrist and about earthquakes.

00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:38.317
This is what's coming. Oregon is fixing to have a major earthquake.

00:05:38.318 --> 00:05:51.155
This is stuff because I know God puts these signs. Signs will follow them that believe. Signs will follow them that believe; He said they would.

00:05:51.156 --> 00:06:03.564
And God gives us these things to be a light in the darkness to this world, not to be flaky. What makes us stand out? It's the signs. It's the wonders.

00:06:03.565 --> 00:06:19.871
It's whenever we touch somebody, and they are lost as a goose in the fog, and you lay hands on them, and the power of God sets them free, and they go from glory to glory. There was something to that.

00:06:19.872 --> 00:06:35.342
It's not just watered-down, lukewarm religion that you're getting from stale preachers behind the pulpit, but you're teaching people that Jesus Christ is coming and they need to repent because if they don't, they're going to hell.

00:06:35.343 --> 00:06:49.932
He came to set the captives free. He told us to do the Great Commission: to go into all the world, lay hands on the sick, and they would recover, cast out devils, raise the dead, do all the things that He said we could do.

00:06:49.933 --> 00:07:01.148
Why aren't we seeing it? Because we're not believing it. I want to be a believing believer.

00:07:01.149 --> 00:07:10.624
And when I saw that man, the Lord told me, "If he dies tonight, Brandon, he's going to hell."I had compassion inside of me.

00:07:10.625 --> 00:07:21.913
I wanted to—it would look flaky—but bend down on my knees right then and grab his ankle and say, "If you die tonight, sir, the Lord told me you're going to hell.

00:07:21.914 --> 00:07:27.575
I don't know what it is with you, but God's calling you. God's calling you.

00:07:27.576 --> 00:07:40.719
God's calling your son that's standing next to you."And I feel to intercede and just weep on behalf of your soul because you don't realize how close you are to stepping over.

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:50.088
I don't know what it was about that man, but he came to my house, and I figured he's here for a reason. It's not a coincidence. "Yeah, you messed up my septic.

00:07:50.089 --> 00:07:56.522
Yeah, you did all this stuff, and I'm showing you love because my flesh wants to just be really ugly right now.

00:07:56.523 --> 00:08:04.268
What do you do for a living, sir?""I'm a preacher.""I could be a real jerk right now.

00:08:04.269 --> 00:08:11.803
I really could because of what you did, but I'm going to show you love, and I'm going to pay for it. I'm going to pay for it. It doesn't cost you anything.

00:08:11.804 --> 00:08:27.672
It was an accident."But you have the opportunity right then to show the love of God to somebody, and you can totally lose it because thousands of dollars is a lot, or you can love on somebody because they made a mistake.

00:08:27.673 --> 00:08:36.639
Yeah, it was a costly one, but my point is that's the love that He's talking about in 1 Corinthians 13 right now.

00:08:36.640 --> 00:08:43.358
Not all things are always easy, especially when you're dealing with the world and they mess up your yard and they do all the things that they do.

00:08:43.359 --> 00:08:46.773
And you know what? The one guy came back and made it all right.

00:08:46.774 --> 00:08:51.815
He went out and cleaned up the stuff, and he apologized because it was bad.

00:08:51.816 --> 00:08:57.199
I'm just telling y'all, it was bad. A lot of things. My house is leaking water clear into my bedroom.

00:08:57.200 --> 00:09:04.599
There's a lot going on this last week. Then we made the video last week.

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:11.405
Wednesday evening, we got home from church, did all that, got so excited. Thursday morning, we woke up.

00:09:11.406 --> 00:09:16.063
We're going to make another video for you all, and Braden's computer has completely crashed.

00:09:16.064 --> 00:09:23.158
All of the software, all of it completely gone, wiped out. It's like we got hacked in the middle of the night.

00:09:23.159 --> 00:09:33.224
Literally, the computer won't start, won't do anything. And he goes, 'Daddy, something bad has happened to the computer that we got blessed with.

00:09:33.225 --> 00:09:39.674
It's not working at all.'And I said, 'What happened?'He goes, 'It won't even boot up.

00:09:39.675 --> 00:09:43.803
There's nothing. It won't even do anything.'It was completely frozen.

00:09:43.804 --> 00:09:48.155
Everything about this after we made that video about the energy and everything.

00:09:48.156 --> 00:09:51.594
So, I figured we got hacked. Something happened in the middle of the night.

00:09:51.595 --> 00:09:57.657
I still don't know what happened. So, he had to reboot it back up. He's watching YouTube videos.

00:09:57.658 --> 00:10:05.583
All these little pricks because I know I'm on the right road and I'm going somewhere with this.

00:10:05.584 --> 00:10:15.037
You know you're on the right road when you're getting these little pricks because the enemy is ticked off because I'm putting a kink in his hose and he doesn't like it because I'm teaching a lot of you.

00:10:15.038 --> 00:10:23.043
You know how many people email every day, 'You're teaching me to pray. You're teaching me how to live by faith. I was suicidal.

00:10:23.044 --> 00:10:33.316
My marriage has been restored.'How many people have gotten their lives changed by watching these videos?

00:10:33.317 --> 00:10:39.482
I'm humbled. So many people said, 'I never knew how to pray in the Holy Ghost and baptism.

00:10:39.483 --> 00:10:47.056
I got filled with the Holy Ghost and fire watching these videos and I pray with you every single day.'How many people said, 'I was lukewarm and you turned me around?

00:10:47.057 --> 00:11:05.449
I watch you instead of pastors now because I get more out of your sermons.'I said, 'My God, what an honor that you'd come to listen to me.'But after you get all these little pricks and things, and Braden finally, it was the grace of God watching a YouTube video that we were able to—because he said, 'Daddy, we're going to have to buy a new computer.

00:11:05.450 --> 00:11:10.127
This computer's gone.'And watching a YouTube video, he fixed it.

00:11:10.128 --> 00:11:20.496
Thank God. Took him all day long Thursday. All day long, we didn't have it. And I told him, I said, 'Whatever happens happens, buddy.

00:11:20.497 --> 00:11:31.613
We'll make it work.'Whenever the enemy comes in and he tries to test you to see if he's getting to you by how you react.

00:11:31.614 --> 00:11:46.319
How are you reacting to the septic tank getting run over, the water line, and the water flooding my bathroom and ruining it, and I had to go and fix all that, the boards falling down from the storm?

00:11:46.320 --> 00:12:01.103
All these little things. The enemy tried to get you all in your thoughts, but it all goes back to 1 Corinthians 13.

00:12:01.104 --> 00:12:07.359
Will you walk in love? Will you allow your fruit to shine to men?

00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:19.888
And whenever the devil's trying to get your joy with all these little things and it all adds up, like I said, thousands, and my flesh, like I said, I was—wow.

00:12:19.889 --> 00:12:27.774
Okay. So, whenever all that's coming on you and all that's going on and you have the opportunity to walk in love, right?

00:12:27.775 --> 00:12:36.130
Walk in love. The Bible says, 'Take no thought, saying.'Take no thought, saying.

00:12:36.131 --> 00:12:42.684
Why? Because out of the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks. And the devil cannot read your thoughts.

00:12:42.685 --> 00:12:53.455
The devil can't go around looking, 'Am I getting to him?'So the only way he can know if he's getting to you is by how you're responding on the outside in the natural.

00:12:53.456 --> 00:12:57.942
Because the devil's a flesh devil. He doesn't get anything by the spirit of God.

00:12:57.943 --> 00:13:09.536
He has to move by the flesh. And he's not omnipresent. He is either with you or whatever. He's not like the Holy Spirit, right?

00:13:09.537 --> 00:13:19.713
So, his demons are looking to go back and report to him, 'This worked and this didn't work.'But when you show the love of God, you pass the test. That's what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:13:19.714 --> 00:13:26.086
When you get cut off on the road, when you do these things and people treat you badly at the restaurant—you might have a bad server at the restaurant.

00:13:26.087 --> 00:13:32.239
She might give you bad service and you show love and say, 'I'll give her a good tip anyway.

00:13:32.240 --> 00:13:40.370
She doesn't deserve it.'And you might want to just tell her boss, 'She's the most lousy server I've ever had.

00:13:40.371 --> 00:13:45.899
She didn't get my drinks refilled. She didn't give me good service the whole time.

00:13:45.900 --> 00:14:01.325
I'm telling you what, I want to let this girl have a piece of my mind,'you know, but you go and you say, 'Honey, I know this may not be your calling, but I'm going to bless you anyway and show you love,'you know, 20 bucks or whatever.

00:14:01.326 --> 00:14:06.219
I don't know, that's a big tip, I'm just saying you give them a big tip.

00:14:06.220 --> 00:14:12.479
They may say, 'Hey, I can't believe how I treated you'or whatever.

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:25.700
I don't know, I just try to show God's love until the point of where it's painful to my flesh because there's something more about it in the glory, is what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:14:25.701 --> 00:14:31.695
Where is the glory? Where's the outpouring of the spirit of God? Like we've never seen it before.

00:14:31.696 --> 00:14:42.958
The Lord told me, he said, 'Brandon, Jesus did not do any mighty works until somebody put a demand on it.'Look at what he did with the water turning into wine.

00:14:42.959 --> 00:14:55.763
Mary put a demand on that gift inside of him. But it wasn't time yet.

00:14:55.764 --> 00:15:02.188
30 years, nothing, and then somebody put a demand on it and caused that gift to flourish.

00:15:02.189 --> 00:15:07.932
And that's why I feel like a lot of times, maybe that's where we're at. Maybe it wasn't season yet.

00:15:07.933 --> 00:15:13.233
But the Lord said it's time to put a demand on what is rightfully ours.

00:15:13.234 --> 00:15:17.753
When I was driving around today, he said it's time to put a demand on it.

00:15:17.754 --> 00:15:23.273
It's time for you to expect, because I was driving under a bridge.

00:15:23.274 --> 00:15:27.329
I can't even tell you where I was. I was on Memorial Drive in Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:15:27.330 --> 00:15:35.655
And I was going under the bridge because I was looking at the Range Rovers, I was looking at the Cadillac dealership, I was believing big.

00:15:35.656 --> 00:15:41.599
Looking at those cars and going, 'Look at those cars. That's the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:15:41.600 --> 00:15:46.692
Look at those brand new Escalades, look at those brand new Range Rovers, look at those brand new cars.

00:15:46.692 --> 00:15:53.128
Look at what the world has.'And yes, they have it, but greater is he that is in me. Yes.

00:15:53.129 --> 00:15:56.558
He said he would provide, the wealth of the sinners is laid up for the righteous.

00:15:56.559 --> 00:16:01.423
I believe it. It's a wealth transfer time. Some people don't want to agree with me on that.

00:16:01.424 --> 00:16:09.135
That's fine, stay where you are, but don't criticize me for believing big.

00:16:09.136 --> 00:16:24.608
I was driving underneath the bridge there, and the Lord started talking to me about the angels, and he said, 'Brandon, remember I told you as you're passing under this bridge to believe for angelic visitation in these services?

00:16:24.609 --> 00:16:48.910
Believe for the angels to work with you to bring the body parts.'I told you when we got in prayer, if an octopus can get a new limb and grow back new limbs, if a crab can do it and they're sea-dwelling animals, how much more are you able to believe for a new arm or a new leg or new eyes?

00:16:48.911 --> 00:16:54.576
If they can grow back stuff, why can't we? We're created in his image.

00:16:54.577 --> 00:17:00.518
We're created to be the head over all these things. He said to take dominion and authority over these animals.

00:17:00.519 --> 00:17:06.239
How much more do we have the ability to grow back something? 'Well, I don't believe that.

00:17:06.240 --> 00:17:09.370
We've never seen it.'It's time to believe for the impossible.

00:17:09.371 --> 00:17:20.454
It's time to believe. God forbid. Are we in the last days or not? Are we going to see signs will follow them that believe?

00:17:20.455 --> 00:17:29.460
I'm so done with being a Christian that's just barely, you know, 'Well, we see it, well, we may not.'Every once in a while, it's whatever, man.

00:17:29.461 --> 00:17:34.775
I'm believing for it every day. Let's believe for God to do something every day.

00:17:34.776 --> 00:17:44.249
Believe God for finances, like, we need to look nice for him. We represent the King. He's corrected me about my clothes.

00:17:44.250 --> 00:17:47.986
He's corrected me about a lot of things, saying, "Brandon, you represent me.

00:17:47.987 --> 00:17:52.770
You need to look nice for me. When you go into public, you need to look nice.

00:17:52.771 --> 00:17:59.020
Don't wear your scrubby stuff out and always have holes. Look nice for me.

00:17:59.021 --> 00:18:03.301
Look nice."Why? Because John G. Lake used to look in the mirror.

00:18:03.302 --> 00:18:06.696
He put on a white suit, a white tie, and all these white clothes.

00:18:06.697 --> 00:18:13.882
And he looked and said, "God dwells on the inside of this man, and I represent him.

00:18:13.883 --> 00:18:23.839
I represent the King of Kings and the Lord of Lords. And he dwells on the inside of this man."So I started thinking about what John G.

00:18:23.840 --> 00:18:28.917
Lake did, and he had an appearance of excellence. His car was clean.

00:18:28.918 --> 00:18:34.479
Things looked nice. When you represent the King, you look nice. You clean yourself up.

00:18:34.480 --> 00:18:38.568
You may not have a dime to your name, but a bar of soap only costs so much.

00:18:38.569 --> 00:18:45.450
And you look nice with a bar of soap. You don't have to look scruffy and dirty, with oily hair.

00:18:45.451 --> 00:18:50.072
You can have an appearance of cleanliness, too, because cleanliness is godliness.

00:18:50.073 --> 00:18:56.027
My mom would always say, "Cleanliness is godliness."I say, "Well, you don't have to stink with B.O..

00:18:56.028 --> 00:19:11.185
You can have a bar of soap, scrub your armpits down, and make yourself smell nice."I mean, there's a point of appearance, an appearance of excellence, showing up and believing God for more.

00:19:11.186 --> 00:19:15.439
Believing God for more. Well, this guy said, "I believe in God.

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:20.729
Do you think the Lord wants me to have a new car, brother?"That's what I'm talking about, driving around looking at that.

00:19:20.730 --> 00:19:26.013
That's when I heard Brother Hagin teaching that today. I said, "Let's go look at the Cadillacs.

00:19:26.014 --> 00:19:36.756
Let's go look at the Range Rovers. Let's go look for more."Because he said, "Is it wrong to have a brand new car?

00:19:36.757 --> 00:19:44.784
Is it wrong to not be buying used all the time?"And he said, "You're representing the King. You're representing the King.

00:19:44.785 --> 00:19:55.083
And if you, being evil, give good gifts to your kids, how much more does your Heavenly Father give good gifts to those that love him and are hearing him?

00:19:55.084 --> 00:20:00.489
How much more?"So I started thinking, well, why not believe for bigger?

00:20:00.490 --> 00:20:08.439
Why not believe God for more? Why not believe God for a newer house? Why not believe God for this stuff?

00:20:08.440 --> 00:20:11.272
I believed for this house that I'm living in right now, and it's time.

00:20:11.273 --> 00:20:15.020
And the Lord said, "Brandon, look what I gave you this time last year.

00:20:15.021 --> 00:20:19.008
Look how I took care of you this time last year."I was sitting on my back patio.

00:20:19.009 --> 00:20:25.455
I lived in a shotgun house in Guthrie, Oklahoma. Bad mice coming in.

00:20:25.456 --> 00:20:29.479
We had rodents. We had snakes coming up through the floorboards.

00:20:29.480 --> 00:20:39.286
Our house had mold so bad we were falling through the foundation of the floor. Lived there for 22 years.

00:20:39.287 --> 00:20:52.793
22 years my kids, all of them born in there, lived there all those years, being a janitor at the church, making nothing, believing God, believing God.

00:20:52.794 --> 00:20:57.248
And the Lord said, "Stay here. Take care of your grandma."I took care of my grandmother all that time.

00:20:57.249 --> 00:21:02.940
I complained—I'm not going to lie to y'all, I did complain to the Lord. "Lord, I need something better.

00:21:02.941 --> 00:21:15.826
My family—the mold and mildew smell in here is so bad, all the things that we dealt with for so many years."But God came through and got us this house we're living in now.

00:21:15.827 --> 00:21:22.857
23 years. And people say, "Well, Brandon, your house is nice now."But you don't know what I came from. You don't know what God did.

00:21:22.858 --> 00:21:30.713
I never get mad at somebody's blessing whenever you see what they have and where they are, because you don't know what seeds they sowed to get what they've got.

00:21:30.714 --> 00:21:43.648
I rejoice whenever I see a preacher have more. I rejoice whenever I see my brother and sister get a brand new car, because you don't know what seeds they sacrificed to get what they got.

00:21:43.649 --> 00:21:49.690
You don't know what prayers they prayed. You don't know what they gave.

00:21:49.691 --> 00:22:09.918
Do we not believe that the Bible is true, that he gives back 30, 60, and a hundredfold? Why do we get mad when we see somebody get blessed?

00:22:09.919 --> 00:22:11.905
If the Bible is true and he gives back 30, 60, and a hundredfold, why aren't more of us walking in increase?

00:22:11.906 --> 00:22:18.168
Is it because we are ashamed of what he's given us? We don't want to—"Oh, well, we kind of live down and out.

00:22:18.169 --> 00:22:25.397
We just got to barely get by.""I took the vow of poverty."I'm going to tell you this: you're a fool.

00:22:25.398 --> 00:22:31.042
I do not want to receive a vow of poverty. I'm not taking no vow of poverty.

00:22:31.043 --> 00:22:44.478
If the Bible says that the windows of heaven are open over us and he poured out a blessing that we don't have room enough to receive it all, how much more can we walk in it, to not walk by just barely?

00:22:44.479 --> 00:22:49.685
That's why I'm believing God for crypto to take off like a rocket. I talked to a dear sister.

00:22:49.686 --> 00:22:57.474
She lives in Florida, and she said she's believing for big, Brandon, and she's wanting to retire.

00:22:57.475 --> 00:23:02.937
She had all these big desires of believing God to have exceeding. She works for the TSA and all this stuff.

00:23:02.938 --> 00:23:12.629
She told me, she said, "I work for the TSA, worked there for like twenty-some, 30 years or something like that, but I'm believing God to do something big."And I thought, "You inspire me.

